desc_short	-----								In Pro Basketball Manager 2016 US edition you will take the reins of a North American pro team or college side and compete in their respective championships. Outside competition, you must manage recruitment, finances and training while, on game day, you must take control of your players and lead your team to the top of the rankings.							
developer									Cyanide					,			Umix Studios								
